%h2 Simultaneously search Google Bookmarks
%h5 Set your bookmarklet preferences and create your bookmarklet:
%form{ :action => "/google/bookmarklet", :method => "post"}
  %fieldset
    %ol
      %li
        %label{:for => "new_window"} Which search result should open in a new window?
        %input{:type => "radio", :name => "newwin", :value => "google"} Google
        %input{:type => "radio", :name => "newwin", :value => "bookmarks", :checked => "checked"} Google Bookmarks
    %input{:type => "submit", :value => "Create"}